In these troubled times, the world perhaps needs a bit of cheer, and what
better than the bright, sparkling colors of
[Holi](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holi), the festival of Spring, to renew
our optimism, hopes and joy.

Here are some images of this colorful festival, being played with zest across
India.

